text: How long has Okada been champion?
Who is the youngest IWGP Heavyweight Champion?

Kazuchika Okada is a Japanese professional wrestler. He is signed to New Japan Pro-Wrestling, where he is the current IWGP Heavyweight Champion in his fifth reign. Okada's fourth reign with the championship is the longest in history at 720 days; he also holds the record for most successful title defenses with twelve.
